      "title": "The weather suddenly changed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Meteorology has issued a warning about heavy rain and strong winds. Accordingly, heavy rains exceeding 100 mm are expected in Sabaragamuwa province, Mahanuwara, Nuwara Eliya, Galle and Matara districts as well, the department said."
